<title>USA: CCF Holding plans to buyback common stock.</title>
<headline>CCF Holding plans to buyback common stock.</headline>
<dateline>JONESBORO, Ga 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>CCF Holding Co said Thursday it planned to repurchase up to 10 percent of its 1.0 million outstanding common shares on the open market.  </p>
<p>CCF, the holding company of Clayton County Federal Savings and Loan Association, said it was waiting to get approval before buying up to 1,101,766 shares.</p>
<p>The company's board authorized it to repurchase shares on July 3.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212 859-1610</p>
